          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780380715893" href="/book/show/988507.A_Soldier_of_the_Great_War">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/992712-delille?shelf=religion">religion</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/992712-delille?shelf=political">political</a>, 
