        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer101368581" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16115041563902499217">I tend to race through books, which was a huge mistake with this one. A Soldier of the Great War needs to be read slowly with each description and each passage savored. It is a gorgeous, almost achingly beautiful book. If someone could &quot;paint&quot; a book, this would be it. True art. Reading this book is like taking a drug... you walk away seeing everything from a different -- and spiritually deeper -- angle. This book makes me realize how asleep we are, and how much richer life is than we ever stop </span>
  <span id="freeText16115041563902499217" style="display:none">I tend to race through books, which was a huge mistake with this one. A Soldier of the Great War needs to be read slowly with each description and each passage savored. It is a gorgeous, almost achingly beautiful book. If someone could "paint" a book, this would be it. True art. Reading this book is like taking a drug... you walk away seeing everything from a different -- and spiritually deeper -- angle. This book makes me realize how asleep we are, and how much richer life is than we ever stop to notice. But also, how meaningless we are. <br /><br />Sobering. Heartbreaking. Stunning.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16115041563902499217" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

