        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1249985324" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9403927729805337555">An old man was reminiscing mostly about his WWI experiences as an Italian soldier. At times I wished he would hurry up and get on with the story lines that interested me. Then at others I wanted to know more about his life and his thoughts. This book is not for everyone. If you like Joseph Heller (Catch-22),Vonnegut &amp; Remarque you might enjoy this novel. It is about 800 pages so I recommend it to patient readers. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


