      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Robin Mccormack" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Robin Mccormack" href="/user/show/6734331-robin-mccormack">Robin Mccormack</a>
      </span>

        rated it
